<p style="text-align: center;">&#8212;&#8211;</p>
<p><a href="http://endoftheamericandream.com/archives/ididntjoin-stunning-photos-of-u-s-service-members-publicly-saying-no-to-war-with-syria/stay-out-of-syria" rel="attachment wp-att-3712"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3712" alt="Stay Out Of Syria" src="http://endoftheamericandream.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Stay-Out-Of-Syria-460x509.jpg" width="460" height="509" /></a></p>
