<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" width="550"><p><a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IdidntJoin&amp;src=hash">#IdidntJoin</a> 3 <a href="http://t.co/gOozxPOR7m">pic.twitter.com/gOozxPOR7m</a></p>
